{"tid":1563364,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"睇左消防記招 講到尾太子站核心都係一個問題","createTime":"2019-09-12T11:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T18:25:51.000Z","uid":160887,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9367da8e8d74abc6613e60c51c0d011339bb1f","tid":1563364,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">班狗莫名其妙帶走左三個傷者機會大定消防數錯人頭機會大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇左陣消防記招 最關鍵都係答唔到點解數多三個<br />\n<br />\n但問題係<br />\n<br />\n即使係消失左三個人 救護都係一早睇過果幾個人既傷勢<br />\n<br />\n如果真係比救護+18個消防見到有三個手足死左件事重壓到落黎既機會太低<br />\n<br />\n姐係話如果冇數錯 只可以理解為有三個冇死甚至冇危殆既傷者消失左<br />\n<br />\n而呢一點我係R爆頭都諗唔明 唔通錯手打傷左三隻鬼？定話班狗帶走佢地再打死？<br />\n<br />\n開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecf3018398de359151eaad281dddd1d7cc3f9b6","tid":1563364,"uid":80503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"講咁多做咩 公開CCTV咪得囉"},{"pid":"b63a79b2d32dd5fedc00a405cf718655a4da3000","tid":1563364,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"其實兩位都講到好明<br />\n我接觸到既都盡接觸唔到果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4fc6f73fb0ac11bef222200b43686b40b6109c","tid":1563364,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: cen